{"tid":886504,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"「認真問」四大天王唱功點排？","createTime":"2018-11-02T06:55:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T12:23:22.000Z","uid":206673,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"010f2d8ede6ebf56de3a2edc55e101d70f0aacf7","tid":886504,"uid":206673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T06:55:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vaZhdpD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvaZhdpD.png&h=50c82936&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n四個紅遍亞洲華人地區嘅天王<br />\n<br />\n張學友最勁應該唔使講，呢個應該無人反對<br />\n但我比較想知點排老黎、填海華同國貨城<br />\n<br />\n老黎-唱情歌無得輸，情深款款，聽到耳仔出油，好有feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有各種各樣電音，當年hit爆全城，落親disco必播老黎快歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n代表作:我這樣愛你、如果可以再見你、越夜越有機⋯<br />\n<br />\n填海-好多悲情歌，個人認為佢唱歌好有氣勢，唱腔都幾特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n代表作:忘情水、你是我的女人、冰雨<br />\n<br />\n國貨-勁歌熱舞代表人物，但唱功稍弱，偶有情歌但未算出名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n代表作:櫻花個首(唔記得咩名)、二十六夜、狂野之城<br />\n<br />\n我自己咁排<br />\n學友＞老黎＞填海＞國貨<br />\n<br />\n真係好懷念個陣仲讀緊中學，日日就係聽住佢地啲歌度過，青春啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J0AwhUw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ0AwhUw.png&h=9c6b1858&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"577fd1e871c5c3277566a7d8061a7eedc4d84527","tid":886504,"uid":7699,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T06:56:29.000Z","msg":"學友&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;老黎&gt;&gt;是撚但"},{"pid":"f2bfe2847570113ddad6240b99d66b835db47425","tid":886504,"uid":10922,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"577fd1e871c5c3277566a7d8061a7eedc4d84527","tid":886504,"uid":7699,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T06:56:29.000Z","msg":"學友&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;老黎&gt;&gt;是撚但"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T06:57:21.000Z","msg":"